text: "Win Some Lose Some is a 2000 song by Robbie Williams and is the fifth and final single from his second studio album I've Been Expecting You. It was only released in New Zealand where it made number 7 on the charts. Nicole Appleton from All Saints provides "I love you baby" on the intro. It was included on the New Zealand version of Greatest Hits album in 2004. ==Track listing== New Zealand CD single # "Win Some Lose Some" – 4:18 # "Phoenix from the Flames" – 4:02 # "The Full Monty Medley" (with Tom Jones) – 5:28 ==References== Category:2000 songs Category:Robbie Williams songs
title: Win Some Lose Some
